                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320906-441-off2481 t18320906-441-cd2482"></join>, 1 crown, 8 half-crowns, 25 shillings, and 9 sixpences, the monies of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18320906-441-victim3557" type="victimName">
